    <!-- Translation notes -->
    <h3>Translation notes</h3>
    <p>Hefferon proves the dimension theorem (any two bases have the same size) via the Replacement Lemma. The chapter also covers coordinates, change of basis, and the row space / column space distinction. This page focuses on definitions and intuition. For the proofs, see the original text.</p>

